OL,3,CFormer Lancs and England fast bowler
OL,4,CPeter Lever has died at the age of 84
OL,6,FThe former Lancashire and England fast
OL,7,Fbowler Peter Lever has died at the age
OL,8,Fof 84, his former club has announced.
OL,10,FIn a posting on its X account
OL,11,FLancashire broke the news, writing:
OL,12,F"We are deeply saddened by the news
OL,13,Fthat Peter Lever has passed away, aged
OL,14,F84.
OL,16,F"Peter was inducted into our Hall of
OL,17,FFame last year after playing 301 First-
OL,18,FClass matches between 1960 and 1976 `
OL,19,Ftaking 796 wickets. Our thoughts are
OL,20,Fwith his family and friends."
