OL,6,FPeter Lever's wife Ros told the BBC:
OL,7,F"It is with a heavy heart and deep
OL,8,Fsadness that Peter Lever has passed
OL,9,Faway peacefully today. A beloved
OL,10,Fhusband, father, grandfather and great-
OL,11,Fgrandfather.
OL,13,F"An enormous thank you to everyone
OL,14,Fthat has been caring and considerate
OL,15,Fin supporting Peter through these
OL,16,Fdifficult recent times."
