OL,3,CFormer Lancs and England fast bowler
OL,4,CPeter Lever has died at the age of 84
OL,6,FLancashire-born Lever was a prolific
OL,7,Ffigure for the Red Rose during a long
OL,8,Fand fruitful domestic career,
OL,9,Ffinishing with over 1,000 professional
OL,10,Fwickets.
OL,12,FNo stranger to the international stage
OL,13,Fhe played 17 Tests and 10 one day
OL,14,Finternationals for his country `
OL,15,Fincluding the historic inaugural one-
OL,16,Fday international in 1971 ` and was
OL,17,Fpart of the triumphant Ashes tour of
OL,18,F1970-71.
