OL,3,CFormer Lancs and England fast bowler
OL,4,CPeter Lever has died at the age of 84
OL,6,FHe returned Down Under in 1975, when
OL,7,Fhe claimed career-best figures of six
OL,8,Ffor 38 at the Melbourne Cricket Ground.
OL,10,FIn the pre-helmet era, Lever struck
OL,11,FNew Zealand's Ewen Chatfield on the
OL,12,Fhead with a bouncer during a Test in
OL,13,FAuckland, with emergency medical
OL,14,Ftreatment saving the tailender's life
OL,15,Fafter his heart briefly stopped.
